title: Spoiler: WWE NXT Superstar Loses A "Loser Leaves NXT" Match For Next Month
text:
By Marc Middleton | February 22, 2017 
It appears "The Drifter" Elias Samson is on his way out of WWE NXT as he lost a "Loser Leaves NXT" match to Kassius Ohno at tonight's tapings from the campus of the University of Central Florida. The match should air on the March 8th NXT episode. Fans sang "goodbye" to Samson after the match while Ohno destroyed his guitar.
No word yet on if this means Samson is headed for the main roster or not.
